From 9cf73d3038e327b5d58275d5e457d5831091d060 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Credora QA Bot <credora-qa@picasocode>
Date: Fri, 19 Jun 2026 12:18:58 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(seo): comprehensive SEO optimization (no content
 changes)
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

7 workstreams shipped, zero visible content changes:

1. META + OG (every page)
   - Added metadataBase (fixes OG URL warnings)
   - Added Twitter card metadata (summary_large_image) on all 16 layouts
   - Added canonical URLs (alternates.canonical) on all 16 layouts
   - Added locale (en_IN) and siteName to all OG tags
   - Added robots meta with googleBot directives
   - Added formatDetection (disables unwanted phone/email autolinking)
   - Added themeColor via viewport export
   - Expanded keywords with high-intent search terms (business loan Chennai,
     collateral free business loan, etc.)

2. SCHEMA.ORG JSON-LD (rich results eligibility)
   - Organization schema (sitewide, in root layout)
   - LocalBusiness/FinancialService schema with Chennai address, geo
     coordinates, opening hours, and service area (sitewide)
   - WebSite schema with SearchAction (sitewide)
   - Service schema on every service + product page (10 pages)
   - FAQPage schema on every service page (4 pages, all FAQs)
   - BreadcrumbList schema on every page (16 pages)
   - Article schema on every blog post (6 posts, with datePublished,
     author, keywords, articleSection)

3. SITEMAP + ROBOTS
   - src/app/sitemap.ts auto-generates /sitemap.xml from NAV_ENTRIES
     + all blog posts (23 URLs total)
   - src/app/robots.ts replaces static public/robots.txt with
     dynamic rules: allow all major bots, disallow /api/, reference
     sitemap, allow social crawlers (Twitterbot, facebookexternalhit,
     LinkedInBot) for proper OG rendering

4. SEMANTIC HTML (verified)
   - H1 verified present on home page (motion.h1 -> <h1> in DOM)
   - All images have descriptive alt text (no empty alts)
   - Heading hierarchy H1 > H2 > H3 verified

5. OG IMAGES
   - Generated 18 branded 1200x630 PNG OG images using Credora palette
     (navy + blue + lime accents)
   - One default + 17 page-specific (home, about, contact, blog,
     services, 4 service detail, products, 5 product detail,
     referral-partner, emi-calculator)
   - Each image includes logo, page title, subtitle, and site URL

6. LOCAL SEO (Chennai office)
   - Full LocalBusiness schema with:
     * Postal address (Anna Nagar West Extension, Padi, Chennai 600050)
     * Geo coordinates (13.085, 80.2154)
     * Opening hours (Mon-Sat 9 AM - 6 PM)
     * Service area (India + Tamil Nadu + Chennai)
   - Enables 'business loan Chennai' / 'MSME loan advisor near me'
     query eligibility in Google Maps + local pack

7. BLOG SEO
   - New src/app/blog/[id]/layout.tsx server component with
     generateStaticParams + generateMetadata
   - Per-post title, description, keywords, canonical, OG, Twitter
   - Article schema with datePublished, author, tags
   - BreadcrumbList schema (Home > Blog > Post Title)

8. ANALYTICS PLACEHOLDER
   - src/components/Analytics.tsx — GA4 placeholder, env-var gated
   - Set NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX to enable
   - Ships zero tracking code until env var is set

NEW FILES (10):
- src/lib/seo.ts            — central SEO config (site URL, contact, social, nav)
- src/lib/schema.ts         — schema.org builders (Org, LocalBiz, Service, FAQ, etc.)
- src/components/JsonLd.tsx — JSON-LD script tag renderer
- src/components/Analytics.tsx — GA4 placeholder
- src/components/ServiceSeo.tsx — Service + FAQ + Breadcrumb injector
- src/components/ProductSeo.tsx — Service + Breadcrumb injector for products
- src/components/PageSchema.tsx — WebPage + Breadcrumb for static pages
- src/app/sitemap.ts        — auto /sitemap.xml
- src/app/robots.ts         — auto /robots.txt
- src/app/blog/[id]/layout.tsx — per-post metadata + Article JSON-LD
- public/og/*.png           — 18 OG images

MODIFIED FILES (16):
- Root layout: metadataBase, Twitter cards, OG defaults, sitewide JSON-LD, GA4
- 5 service layouts: canonical, OG images, Twitter, ServiceSeo injection
- 6 product layouts: canonical, OG images, Twitter, ProductSeo injection
- About/Contact/Referral/Blog/EMI layouts: canonical, OG images, Twitter, PageSchema

Build verified: 'next build' compiles cleanly, all 30 pages prerender,
/sitemap.xml and /robots.txt are now valid routes, all 6 blog posts
statically pre-rendered with per-post metadata.
